[DESCRIPTION] This file should contain make targets for common development tasks.

Expected targets (descriptive only, no actual commands):

- setup: Environment setup and dependency installation
- clean: Remove temporary files, cache, and build artifacts
- lint: Run code linters and formatters
- test: Run test suite
- format: Auto-format code
- check: Run all checks (lint, type-check, test)
- run: Run the main application
- export-youtube: Export podcast for YouTube
- export-spotify: Export podcast for Spotify
- help: Display available targets

